Title: Enhance detection of postfix installation
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: agents
Date: 1667808761
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.2.0b1

We now can detect the PID of a running postfix instance if it is not installed in `/var/spool/postfix`.
To do this we search for the pid file in the queue directory as reported by `postconf`.

You can find the new instances after updating the check mk agent.

